 1=\int _{ 1 }^{ \infty  }{ \frac { b }{ x(2x+b) } dx }=\ln(b+2)-\ln(2)=\ln(\frac{b+2}{2}) 
 \implies \frac{b+2}{2}=e \implies b=2 e -2 \implies a+b= 2 e-2 .
